{"type": "article", "id": 22743, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-24T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 4284, "name": "北欧"}, {"id": 23849, "name": "MSDS"}, {"id": 23850, "name": "Flank Pty Ltd"}, {"id": 23851, "name": "Backbone Branding"}, {"id": 23852, "name": "Yaroslav Misonzhnikov"}, {"id": 17946, "name": "Joey Ruiter"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122214Rs4EYPngrvkuipZf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Source Materials  by MSDS </h2>\n<p>这是加拿大设计事务所 MSDS 带来的家具系列，也是一组北欧式的极简家具。椅子借用了 17 世纪温莎椅的风格，椅腿和靠背微微倾斜，但三根腿的结构让这把椅子更加简洁。边桌用木材、铝和石材三种材料设计一种相似的造型，都从横梁上延伸出新的支撑，却有不同的表达方式，很有趣。陶制的桌灯像微微打开的花瓣，带来略有渐变的温和光影。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134402nLAtquQzI5iPUpfo.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134402XQw79cFi0N6thUaM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344035W4xULlfgZdY9Fpv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64102564\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344046SEh0FzH1JGD9LYr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134404zVIQMPrvLpSDxoy6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134405bOJmLckuNFTsVrgD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Savannah table by Monica Förster &amp; Erik Jørgensen</h2>\n<p>这是瑞典女设计师 Monica Förster  为家具品牌 Erik Jørgensen 设计的咖啡桌，与她一年前设计的沙发是配套的，因而结构类似。她使用细木腿做结构，微微叉开，简洁优雅。桌腿和桌面有一根横梁似的木条连接，露出来圆形截面，增加了温和的性格。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344062RMe4wV8UdBGuKTm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134407uzMXhJmqn6BKDPir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50961538\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134407s1Yq36nDaHrRP87W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58974359\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134408bjdxQ1gNf6crJiy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134409TbmfLkDjSyO6e8ad.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Khokhloma by Yaroslav Misonzhnikov</h2>\n<p>这是俄罗斯设计师 Yaroslav Misonzhnikov 带来的一套实木日用品，包括梳子、镜子和扇子。这一系列都带有俄罗斯的民间元素，梳子和镜子的把手都是半月形的，让自然的木纹成为一种装饰，非常秀丽。扇子是在实木圆框中使用了蕾丝织面，也是在俄罗斯的传统用法中结合了简约的现代风格。<a href=\"http://misonzhnikov.com/portfolio/projects/katerina.html\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134409kDKWdqTZjztM3GXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134410KkJ9XbViaYAew7fU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134410un0lVKaAdieWw36t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134411GX4ZpO1VYBRz6axq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134412jPpiu7628qKfszYc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>MEMOBOTTLE™ By Flank Pty Ltd</h2>\n<p>这是一个水瓶，有点像一瓶香水。采用透明的不含 BPA 的塑料制作，表面没有彩色的图样，近似长方体的外形自有一种干净和精致，它同样也适合夹在书中。设计者来自澳大利亚，他们忧心于人们对水瓶的浪费而设计了这款瓶子，A5、A6 分别可容纳 750ml、375ml ，后者可以直接装在口袋里。有黑色或白色两种盖子选择，售价 22 澳元起，<a href=\"http://www.memobottle.com/pages/thememobottlestory\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134413g7sUwxLvGKSYJHMT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134413zCYfXlbL04tWexcg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134414QmbyASrDzqtvXOoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134415hcmMfStqLkogp8JO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134416bw6LCX8p4maRYU0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Lo-Ruiter by Joey Ruiter </h2>\n<p>这是美国设计师 Joey Ruiter 带来的滑板，使用略带方形的木板制作。特别在于中间和四个角落的镂空，让它显得干净利落。4 个角落对应了滚轮的位置，倾斜时恰好卡在空出来的地方，而中间的镂空是用方便脚尖插入帮助暂停的。售价 295 美元，<a href=\"http://www.blessthisstuff.com/stuff/vehicles/misc/lo-ruiter-longboard/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134417Ut8Oyjf34zqPbK5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68041237\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134418i17QRqGBU8pdDzJ6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67802385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134418ChDBUnOocGZyTdI4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67802385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021344194fJkcOi5sqDBYawd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40374787\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134419Wkz6dygloJARhj23.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40374787\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SIS by Backbone Branding</h2>\n<p>这是一个可容纳 2 升果汁的包装，它的外形近似花蕊。瓶身像是三个波浪连起来的，削弱了大容量的笨重感，反而增加了光泽度。其中一个凸出来的结构镂空，成为手柄，可以增加倾倒的稳定性。多个水瓶可以沿着三角形结构的凹凸侧面放置，也比圆形水瓶更稳定。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134420xmf6OasXt7guZrqi.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134421815xZUDjXyVk3PpF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134422Nv8dkIy290Y4hgSp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134422SivU8PIanuzcNyXZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66018519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134424jPw30ChWimt7D4s5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}